<title>bnạdyk tʿạla</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bnạdyk tʿạla yạrby ly bnạdyk wʿạrfk ḥạss bạlly fy
 bnạdyk ʿsẖạn ḍạqt ạldnyạ by bnạdy bạ̹ymạn mḥtạj lk ḥwạly
 ạlqrạr- mạtsbnysẖ yạrb mḥtạj ạ̹lyk tʿạla wkẖdny byn ạ̹ydyk
 ạrfʿny brwḥy fwq jnạḥyk wṭyr
 kẖdẖny mʿạk ạ̉bʿd mkạn kẖlyny fy ḥḍnk zy zmạn
 nsyny ạlyạ̉s ạlly mn gẖyrk kbyr
 2- yạ yswʿ ạ̉nạ mḥtạj lk ạ̉twb fy ḥyạty yạ yswʿ ạ̉nạ mḥtạj lk
 wbqwlhạ fy ṣlạty wạ̉nạ mạdd ạ̹ydy rạfʿhạ lyk
 bạṣrkẖ bạ̉ʿly̱ ṣwty bnạdyk</lyrics>
</song>